g.text: * SAM Accelerate helps to reduce latency while deploying resources to AWS
* sam sync : sync code and infra
* sam sync --code : sync code changes without updating infra (bypass cloudformation, update in seconds)
* sam sync --code --resource AWS::Serverless::Function : Sync only all Lambda functions and their dependencies
* sam sync --watch: monitor for file changes and automatically synchronize when changes are detected.
